| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5705 — Recovery Inhibition (dispossessor)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0a04343e-aebe-5fbf-837a-2178cfacf1d7"
